fareGroups.priceRemarks:
Included in your Comfort fare:

•  Check in 15kg baggage allowance
•  Carry on one bag max 7kg. 
•  Choice of continental or Indian cuisine non veg or veg. 
•  Spacious seats with a pitch of 33 inches. 
•  Earn miles when you fly.

Disclaimer:

1. Refer to fare rules for specific booking terms and conditions.
2. Please note that if the flight is operated by another airline then the onboard product or service maybe different to that described above
3. Ticketed Baggage Allowance takes precedence over Branded fares baggage allowance, and is always honored in AI Check-in counters

Included in your Comfort Plus fare:

•  Check in 15kg baggage allowance
•  Carry on one bag max 7kg
•  Choice of continental or Indian cuisine non veg or veg
•  Spacious seats with a pitch of 33 inches 
•  No Rebooking charges if done 72 Hrs. prior departure 
•  Lower cancellation fee if cancelled 72 Hrs. prior departure 
•  Earn miles when you fly.
